{"tid":1432602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵啲新嘢玩，你唔悶，街坊，觀眾都悶喇 (re-post, 之前太花)","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T10:32:43.000Z","uid":282797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e743c3e879f16000e82061385a192883bf49285","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"Re-post (接受意見，改後重po)<br />\n大家好，我係P牌，我有嘢想講。不喜勿插 sor.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家發夢都發咗好耐，我哋係時候攪啲新嘢。我哋唔悶，和理非，街坊都悶， <span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最怕悶</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴晚咁，玩吓觀星筆幾創新，又有noise，唔洗吓吓破壞，始終香港人都有潔癖，攪得多未必支持，又悶。<br />\n<br />\n另外，而家啲人話我哋發夢去攪啲狗，係夢境宣泄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔係齋宣泄，我哋係想表達不滿</span>！！！ <strong>宣泄係唔理性</strong>，<strong>我哋要話比人知我哋係理性</strong>，要用行為去表達，費事比人亂講，做新聞。最憎啲人亂講！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓我有咩建議，咩都試吓，唔好悶襯<br />\n<br />\n太多嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">自己做住一兩個先啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 首先，<strong>宣揚帶口罩</strong>，將帶口罩成為潮流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變成平常事，好似着3咁。冇事都可以帶，每日做，任何人都做，當口罩變成著3咁，帶口罩就唔再突出。其實帶口罩有好多好處，嗰啲唔關事嘅大媽，亞叔成日乜都影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帶口罩可以保護自己，特別係出活動時。帶口罩普遍咗，仲可以保護埋發夢嘅手足。<strong>帶口罩保護自己，保護別人</strong>。我哋可以可以攪吓口罩日(例如逄星期三)，甚至口罩月，變成普及。<br />\n<br />\n2. 全民零消費 / 不消費藍店<br />\n不消費藍店，呢個已經攪得唔錯，好多藍店真係少咗好多客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家啲藍店都唔敢亂出聲支持正苦，驚冇生意。我哋要繼續推，要令所有店知道<strong>支持我哋有幫襯，唔支持冇幫襯</strong> (呢個向藍絲學嘅)。<br />\n<br />\n3. 紅底銀行更加要做嘢，佢哋大把<strong>黑材料</strong>揾吓出嚟，人自然會走，或者去攞吓錢都好。黑材料唔一定要新嘅，舊聞都得，新定舊好少人睇得咁清楚，就算係舊又點，即係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有發生過</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個有銀行傳唔掂，即滯提，香港人最驚冇錢。記得通知媽媽，姨媽，姑媽，婆婆，格離屋啲嬸嬸知。但唔洗吓吓最大嗰間先，慢慢嚟，一定到佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揾<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸舊聞炒番起</span>佢，例如毒奶粉，收村等都係好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，等香港人記得大陸啲偉大事蹟。香港人善忘，等我哋幫佢回顧！<br />\n<br />\n知你哋懶到出汁，比定幾條link你哋用住先<br />\n標題可以係 &quot;冤獄昨天他坐，明天你坐！&quot; &quot;毒奶你不怕嗎? 昨天大陸B，明天香港B！&quot; 之類啦，你哋自己諗！<br />\n<strong>【大灣夢●維權一】港人深圳祖屋遭強拆 大陸官權大過法:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190410/59468799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F59468799&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO729V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=916c90a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F59468799&h=5700839f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190410/59468799</a><br />\n<strong>【毒奶粉受害人被指敲詐】 【坐牢五年獲平反卻已家不成家】</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=663606407164764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D663606407164764&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO729V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=7d67b2b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=663606407164764</a><br />\n<strong>《大陸毒奶十年‧傷未癒》結石寶寶十年病纏身 家長維權千日未了願</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hs3nexr8W2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhs3nexr8W2g&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO729V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=3315442e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hs3nexr8W2g</a><br />\n<strong>三聚氰胺毒奶粉事件遺害10年 結石寶寶父親：為治病耗盡家財</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2190549/%E4%B8%89%E8%81%9A%E6%B0%B0%E8%83%BA%E6%AF%92%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%81%BA%E5%AE%B310%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%80%E7%B5%90%E7%9F%B3%E5%AF%B6%E5%AF%B6%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E6%B2%BB%E7%97%85%E8%80%97%E7%9B%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%B2%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2190549%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2581%259A%25E6%25B0%25B0%25E8%2583%25BA%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B2%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B310%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A6%25AA%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2597%2585%25E8%2580%2597%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B2%25A1&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO729V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=efa442f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2190549/%E4%B8%89%E8%81%9A%E6%B0%B0%E8%83%BA%E6%AF%92%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%81%BA%E5%AE%B310%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%80%E7%B5%90%E7%9F%B3%E5%AF%B6%E5%AF%B6%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E6%B2%BB%E7%97%85%E8%80%97%E7%9B%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%B2%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 攪吓真揾星夜都唔錯，雖然想係香港觀星真係難過登月球 (多謝大財團，光污染)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。越難揾，越要揾，唔洗吓吓狗房嘅，觀星咩地方都可以揾。自己諗吓咩地方啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">但真係唔好騷擾街坊(認真，街坊咁好)，我哋唔做狗行為！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">呢個有風險，小心使用！！</span>唔想狗偷懶，去每區狗房投訴又得（不過要身份証，要小心），日日投訴唔同人，邊個hit，投訴邊個，邊區摧淚，投訴邊區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要有大人齊齊去，唔係比佢哋玩番轉頭，佢哋蝦細路，只驚大人。記住要一人一個投訴 ，放工又可以做。有狗嘢號碼仲好！<strong>人哋以為我哋去開戰，我哋去投訴！玩轉party！</strong><br />\n<br />\n暫時係諗到咁多，咩都試吓！要文武雙全，武完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家文吓，用吓其他方法，要比surprise人，咁先好玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人好怕悶，又怕攰，街坊個個咁大年紀唔支持得幾多次。吓吓攪到街坊受傷，我哋都唔過意得去。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1, 3最易做，4最好玩<br />\n<strong>表達吓你最想做邊啲啦！</strong>"},{"pid":"c94c79c0a11abfe4da5b4dde06b829abb69630ab","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c2acda97edaa82d5e57a2acff2da0c67f8f82af9","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"投個要啦"},{"pid":"47d3333dcf746d3db5dd818b3405e9f8ae00ce25","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2acda97edaa82d5e57a2acff2da0c67f8f82af9","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"投個要啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"投個<span style=\"color: red;\">票</span>啦"},{"pid":"a59a1f1b5b6af6a99cca0a4c15a4a41b08cd4dd2","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2bb21e3836542311f8f288fd07984d0ba6f2e67","tid":1432602,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cddc03e3ec183cc6dfa28cf0890f519bb82f17f","tid":1432602,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"推！"}]}